Usage: report_sai_constraint [-help] [-area_weight <float>]
                             [-congestion_weight <float>]
                             [-order_weight <float>] [-rule <string>]
                             [-spacing_weight <float>]

-help                          # Prints out the command usage
-area_weight <float>           # Specify area weight (float, optional)
-congestion_weight <float>     # Specify congestion weight (float, optional)
-order_weight <float>          # Specify order weight (float, optional)
-rule <string>                 # Specify rule name (string, optional)
-spacing_weight <float>        # Specify spacing weight (float, optional)